name: god looks in the mirror
description:
When a god looks in the mirror, aspects of itself are simultaneously disseminated from the whole and these parts are reflected back through creation. 

Just as we look into a mirror and look at ourselves in parts, physical and otherwise, gods do this and manifest the ideas it has of itself as tangible elements.

‘Empty’ space is simply the divine mirrors surface. What parts of spirit make you up? All energies are available, usable- what elements make you up? You are always able to siphon from source, what will you choose to take?
